ygData.messageBody:
Well, they've got more than a lot of games. There's several varietys of
engagement rings and wedding rings. There are also two types of champagne
(although one is lore). Maybe if they made the gossimer robe wearable by
all it would be a close approximation :)
Besides, some of us happen to like the Pamela Lee look :)


Elwyn Heartstring
Level 41 Bard
Erollisi Marr
